(x + h)^2 = (x+h)(x+h) = x(x+h)+h(x+h).
x(x + h) = x\cdot x + xh = x^2 + xh
h(x+h) = hx + h\cdot h = hx + h^2.
(x+h)^2 = x^2 + xh + hx + h^2.
hx = xh
(x+h)^2 = x^2 + xh + hx + h^2 = x^2 + xh + xh + h^2 = x^2 + 2xh + h^2.
(x+h)(x+h)=x(x+h)+h(x+h)=\\ =x\cdot x+x\cdot h+h\cdot x+h\cdot h=\\ =x^2+xh+hx+h^2=\\ =x^2+2xh+h^2
